his%20fictional%20team%20has%20the%20same%20name%20and%20some%20indicators%20as%20Pepperdine%3F'%26quot%3B%20Rosenblatt%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrademark%20dilution%2C%20however%2C%20could%20hold%20more%20weight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20complaint%2C%20Pepperdine%20University%20said%20that%20Netflix%20and%20Warner%20Bros.%20Entertainment's%20%26quot%3Bimproper%20use%20of%20the%20asserted%20trademarks%26quot%3B%20could%20%26quot%3Bdilute%2C%20tarnish%2C%20and%20disparage%20Pepperdine's%20reputation%20and%20marks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BParticularly%20because%20the%20Netflix%20show%20has%20content%20that%20is%20so%20at%20odds%20with%20Pepperdine's%20conservative%20values%20and%20religious%20philosophy%2C%20it%20might%20harm%20Pepperdine's%20mark%20in%20that%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20Rosenblatt%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeltz%20said%20the%20trademark%20dilution%20claim%20requires%20proof%20of%20fame%2C%20which%20would%20examine%20whether%20Pepperdine%20University's%20trademarks%20are%20well-known%20and%20being%20diluted%20by%20%26quot%3BRunning%20Point.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2261b072e1-6ecb-4f58-ae23-289ad9a829c3%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20judge%20denied%20the%20university's%20TRO%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20granted%2C%20the%20temporary%20restraining%20order%20against%20Netflix%20and%20Warner%20Bros.%20Entertainment%20would%20have%20barred%20them%20from%20certain%20actions%2C%20including%20airing%20%26quot%3BRunning%20Point%26quot%3B%20episodes%20unless%20they're%20first%20edited%20to%20exclude%20references%20to%20the%20fictitious%20Waves%20team%20and%20the%20university's%20trademarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20memorandum%20on%20Monday%2C%20Netflix%20argued%20against%20the%20temporary%20restraining%20order%2C%20saying%20the%20use%20of%20Waves%20is%20not%20%26quot%3Bexplicitly%20misleading%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20use%20is%20%26quot%3Bartistically%20relevant%2C%26quot%3B%20among%20other%20arguments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20judge%20denied%20Pepperdine%20University's%20request%20two%20days%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222513%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pepperdine%20University%20Waves'%20mascot.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c0a602b8b41a9673f93208%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223770%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPepperdine%20University's%20mascot%20during%20a%20NCAA%20game%20in%202009.%3Cp%3EIcon%20Sports%20Wire%2FCorbis%2FIcon%20Sportswire%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20First%20Amendment%2C%20broadly%20speaking%2C%20allows%20people%20to%20use%20other%20people's%20trademarks%20in%20expressive%20ways%2C%26quot%3B%20Rosenblatt%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20the%20university's%20senior%20vice%20president%2C%20Sean%20Burnett%2C%20said%20the%20case%20against%20Netflix%20and%20Warner%20Bros.%20Entertainment%20will%20%26quot%3Bcontinue%20on%20its%20regular%20course.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20do%20not%20believe%20Netflix%20and%20Warner%20Bros.%20can%20be%20permitted%20to%20take%20the%20Waves%20trademarks%20and%20colors%20we%20have%20used%20for%20almost%2090%20years%20to%20identify%20Pepperdine%20to%20instead%20identify%20the%20team%20that%20is%20the%20subject%20of%20their%20series%2C%26quot%3B%20Burnett%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release.%20%26quot%3BWhile%20we%20are%20disappointed%20with%20today's%20ruling%2C%20we%20believe%20the%20University%20will%20ultimately%20prevail%20and%20prevent%20the%20continued%20unauthorized%20use%20of%20Pepperdine's%20intellectual%20property%20in%20a%20way%20that%20misrepresents%20our%20institution.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Warner%20Bros.%20Entertainment%2C%20Mindy%20Kaling%2C%20Kate%20Hudson%2C%20and%20Jeanie%20Buss%2C%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinside