0Trump%20has%20repeatedly%20criticised%20the%20flow%20of%20illicit%20drugs%20into%20the%20US%2C%20allegedly%20coming%20from%20both%20Canada%20and%20Mexico.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20Trump%20has%20decided%20to%20move%20forward%20with%20the%20imposition%20of%20tariffs%20on%20both%20countries%2C%20starting%20March%204.%20Additionally%2C%20reciprocal%20tariffs%20are%20set%20to%20continue%20with%20full%20force%20from%20April%202.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20Trudeau%20added%20that%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20first%20thing%20on%20tariffs%20is%20to%20emphasise%20that%20our%20government%2C%20and%20indeed%20all%20of%20Team%20Canada%2C%20premiers%2C%20business%20leaders%2C%20community%20leaders%2C%20are%20focused%20on%20one%20thing%2C%20making%20sure%20that%20come%20Tuesday%20and%20for%20the%20weeks%20that%20follow%2C%20there%20are%20no%20tariffs%20imposed%20on%20Canada%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20per%20CBC%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20tariffs%20that%20the%20president%20speaks%20of%20for%20next%20week%20are%20centered%20around%20the%20fentanyl%20crisis%20that%20they're%20facing%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20but%20that%20we%20are%20also%20facing%20in%20Canada%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20concerns%20regarding%20fentanyl%20trafficking%20into%20the%20United%20States%2C%20he%20said%20%26quot%3BAnd%20for%20months%20now%2C%20I've%20been%20emphasising%20that%20less%20than%20one%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20fentanyl%20that%20arrives%20in%20the%20United%20States%20comes%20from%20Canada.%20But%20we%20know%20that%20even%20that%20one%20per%20cent%2C%20or%20less%20than%20one%20per%20cent%2C%20should%20be%20reduced%2C%20which%20is%20why%20we've%20invested%20USD%201.3%20billion%20in%20strengthening%20our%20border%20capacities%20with%20Blackhawk%20helicopters%2C%20with%20drones%2C%20with%2010%2C000%20people%20patrolling%20our%20borders%20and%20keeping%20Canadians%20and%20Americans%20safe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20that%20Canada%20is%20not%20the%20source%20of%20problems%20for%20the%20United%20States%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20on%20February%204%2C%20the%20US%20President%20paused%20tariffs%20on%20imports%20from%20both%20countries%20for%2030%20days%2C%20saying%20that%20he%20had%20secured%20new%20commitments%20from%20the%20two%20countries%20to%20improve%20border%20security.%20The%20pause%20was%20put%20in%20place%20after%20President%20Trump%20said%20he%20spoke%20to%20his%20counterparts%20from%20Mexico%20and%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDrugs%20are%20still%20pouring%20into%20our%20Country%20from%20Mexico%20and%20Canada%20at%20very%20high%20and%20unacceptable%20levels.%20A%20large%20percentage%20of%20these%20Drugs%2C%20much%20of%20them%20in%20the%20form%20of%20Fentanyl%2C%20are%20made%20in%2C%20and%20supplied%20by%20China.%20More%20than%20100%2C000%20people%20died%20last%20year%20due%20to%20the%20distribution%20of%20these%20dangerous%20and%20highly%20addictive%20POISONS%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20Truth%20Social.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20the%20smuggling%20of%20drugs%20across%20the%20border%2C%20Trump%20has%20vowed%20to%20stop%20or%20%26quot%3Bseriously%20limit%26quot%3B%20such%20drugs%2C%20especially%20Fentanyl.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMillions%20of%20people%20have%20died%20over%20the%20last%20two%20decades.%20The%20families%20of%20the%20victims%20are%20devastated%20and%2C%20in%20many%20instances%2C%20virtually%20destroyed.%20We%20cannot%20allow%20this%20scourge%20to%20continue%20to%20harm%20the%20USA%2C%20and%20therefore%2C%20until%20it%20stops%2C%20or%20is%20seriously%20limited%2C%20the%20proposed%20TARIFFS%20scheduled%20to%20go%20into%20effect%20on%20MARCH%204%20will%2C%20indeed%2C%20go%20into%20effect%2C%20as%20scheduled%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20Trump's%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20China%20will%20also%20be%20charged%20an%20additional%2010%20per%20cent%20tariff%20from%20March%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2