ss-standard.com%2Fspecials%2Fbs-events%2Fministries-streamlined-civil-services-reformed-in-10-years-mishra-125022701226_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Donald%20Trump%20Might%20Be%20On%20The%20Losing%20End%20Of%20The%20Mineral%20Deal%20With%20Ukraine%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%20is%20on%20the%20cusp%20of%20finalising%20a%20deal%20with%20Ukraine%2C%20granting%20the%20U.S.%20preferential%20access%20to%20the%20country's%20vast%20raw%20material%20reserves.%20However%2C%20the%20true%20value%20of%20these%20reserves%20is%20shrouded%20in%20uncertainty%2C%20as%20estimates%20are%20based%20on%20outdated%20Soviet-era%20surveys%20that%20failed%20to%20account%20for%20the%20feasibility%20and%20cost%20of%20developing%20these%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20draft%20of%20the%20agreement%20cited%20in%20Economic%20Pravda%2C%20a%20Ukrainian%20newspaper%2C%20stipulates%20that%20Ukraine%20will%20allocate%2050%25%20of%20its%20state-owned%20natural%20resource%20revenues%20to%20a%20fund%20dedicated%20to%20invest%20in%20Ukraine.%20Notably%2C%20this%20deal%20does%20not%20include%20any%20U.S.%20security%20guarantees.%20On%20paper%2C%20the%20U.S.%20appears%20poised%20to%20reap%20significant%20benefits%20from%20this%20agreement%2C%20considering%20Ukraine's%20natural%20resources%20and%20environment%20ministry%20claims%20that%20the%20country's%20bedrock%20contains%20approximately%205%25%20of%20the%20world's%20critical%20raw%20materials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20resources%2C%20including%20graphite%2C%20lithium%2C%20titanium%2C%20beryllium%2C%20and%20uranium%2C%20are%20crucial%20for%20the%20production%20of%20batteries%2C%20radar%20systems%2C%20and%20armour%2C%20which%20are%20essential%20to%20the%20defence%20and%20tech%20industries.%20Securing%20access%20to%20these%20resources%20could%20help%20reduce%20America's%20reliance%20on%20Chinese%20minerals.%20However%2C%20the%20actual%20extent%20of%20Ukraine's%20mineral%20wealth%20remains%20a%20mystery%2C%20with%20only%20around%208%2C000%20of%20the%20country's%2020%2C000%20surveyed%20mineral%20deposits%20and%20sites%20deemed%20viable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20development%20of%20these%20resources%20is%20further%20complicated%20by%20the%20need%20for%20significant%20investment%2C%20estimated%20at%20%2415%20billion%20for%20the%2010%20largest%20known%20mining%20prospects.%20This%20includes%20the%20construction%20of%20mines%2C%20quarries%2C%20and%20processing%20facilities.%20Moreover%2C%20the%20extraction%20process%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20costly%20and%20time-consuming%2C%20with%20the%20Ukrainian%20Geological%20Survey%20estimating%20that%20developing%20the%20Novopoltasvke%20deposit%2C%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20rare%20earth%20sites%20in%20the%20world%2C%20would%20require%20an%20investment%20of%20%24300%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20currently%20dominates%20the%20rare%20earth%20supply%20chain%2C%20processing%20nearly%2090%25%20of%20the%20world's%20rare%20earths.%20The%20U.S.%20and%20other%20major%20producers%20lack%20the%20necessary%20infrastructure%20and%20expertise%20to%20refine%20these%20minerals%2C%20forcing%20them%20to%20rely%20on%20Beijing.%20Developing%20this%20infrastructure%20in%20Ukraine%20would%20take%20years%20and%20likely%20be%20less%20efficient%20than%20shipping%20the%20minerals%20to%20China%20for%20processing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deal%20is%20also%20complicated%20by%20the%20fact%20that%20several%20promising%20mineral%20prospects%20are%20located%20in%20territories%20under%20Russian%20occupation.%20Ukrainian%20Deputy%20Prime%20Minister%20Yulia%20Svyrydenko%20estimates%20that%20Russia%20has%20occupied%20%24350%20billion%20worth%20of%20Ukraine's%20critical%20mineral%20and%20gas%20reserves.%20Trump%20must%20now%20decide%20whether%20to%20increase%20support%20for%20Ukraine%20and%20help%20the%20country%20reclaim%20its%20occupied%20territories%20or%20pursue%20an%20alternative%20deal%20with%20Russia.%20As%20S%26amp%3BP%20Global%20notes%2C%20extracting%20Ukraine's%20rare%20earth%20elements%20might%20not%20be%20profitable%20due%20to%20the%20technical%20challenges%20and%20costs%20involved.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740680700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fef85092o_donald-trump-reuters_625x300_27_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhy-donald-trump-might-be-on-the-losing-end-of-the-mineral-deal-with-ukraine-7809669%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Trump%20must%20now%20decide%20whether%20to%20increase%20support%20for%20Ukraine%20and%20help%20the%20country%20reclaim%20its%20occupied%20territories%20or%20pursue%20an%20alternative%20deal%20with%20Russia.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhy-donald-trump-might-be-on-the-losing-end-of-the-mineral-deal-with-ukraine-7809669%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UK%20PM%20Starmer%20invites%20Donald%20Trump%20for%20state%20visit%20on%20behalf%20of%20King%20Charles%3B%20'would%20be%20an%20honor'%2C%20says%20US%20President%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740680671000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-118611230%2Cimgsize-847208.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fuk-pm-starmer-invites-donald-trump-for-state-visit-on-behalf-of-king-charles-would-be-an-honor-says-us-president%2Farticleshow%2F118610571.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F118610571.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EUK%20PM%20Keir%20Starmer%20invited%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20for%20a%20second%20state%20visit%20to%20Britain%2C%20an%20unprecedented%20gesture.%20Trump's%20acceptance%20followed%20discussions%20on%20the%20Ukraine%20conflict.%20Starmer%20urged%20Trump%20to%20involve%20Kyiv%20and%20European%20leaders%20in%20peace%20talks%2C%20while%20Trump's%20approach%20towards%20Russia%20and%20reevaluating%20US%20foreign%20policy%20stirs%20European%20concerns.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fuk-pm-starmer-invites-donald-trump-for-state-visit-on-behalf-of-king-charles-would-be-an-honor-says-us-president%2Farticleshow%2F118610571.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fuk-pm-starmer-invites-donald-trump-for-state-visit-on-behalf-of-king-charles-would-be-an-honor-says-us-president%2Famp_articleshow%2F118610571.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fuk-pm-starmer-invites-donald-trump-for-state-visit-on-behalf-of-king-charles-would-be-an-honor-says-us-president%2Famp_articleshow%2F118610571.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Cuts%20Overseas%20Development%20Program%20Budgets%20By%20More%20Than%2090%25%3A%20State%20Dept%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States%20has%20dramatically%20cut%20the%20budgets%20of%20overseas%20development%20and%20aid%20programs%2C%20with%20multi-year%20contracts%20pared%20down%20by%2092%20percent%2C%20or%20%2454%20billion%2C%20the%20State%20Department%20said%20Wednesday.%3Cbr%3E%5CnOn%20his%20first%20day%20in%20office%2C%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20signed%20an%20executive%20order%20demanding%20a%20freeze%20on%20all%20US%20foreign%20aid%20for%2090%20days.%20The%20pause%20aimed%20to%20allow%20the%20administration%20to%20review%20overseas%20spending%20with%20an%20eye%20to%20gutting%20programs%20not%20aligned%20with%20Trump's%20%26quot%3BAmerica%20First%26quot%3B%20agenda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20review%20in%20part%20targeted%20multi-year%20foreign%20assistance%20contracts%20awarded%20by%20the%20US%20Agency%20for%20International%20Development%20(USAID)%2C%20with%20the%20vast%20majority%20eliminated%20during%20its%20course.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20conclusion%20of%20a%20process%20led%20by%20USAID%20leadership%2C%20including%20tranches%20personally%20reviewed%20by%20Secretary%20(Marco)%20Rubio%2C%20nearly%205%2C800%20awards%20with%20%2454%20billion%20in%20value%20remaining%20were%20identified%20for%20elimination%20as%20part%20of%20the%20America%20First%20agenda%20--%20a%2092%20percent%20reduction%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20State%20Department%20spokesperson%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20review%20also%20looked%20at%20more%20than%209%2C100%20grants%20involving%20foreign%20assistance%2C%20valued%20at%20more%20than%20%2415.9%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20conclusion%20of%20the%20review%2C%204%2C100%20grants%20worth%20almost%20%244.4%20billion%20were%20targeted%20to%20be%20eliminated%2C%20a%2028%20percent%20reduction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20commonsense%20eliminations%20will%20allow%20the%20bureaus%2C%20along%20with%20their%20contracting%20and%20grants%20officers%2C%20to%20focus%20on%20remaining%20programs%2C%20find%20additional%20efficiencies%20and%20tailor%20subsequent%20programs%20more%20closely%20to%20the%20Administration's%20America%20First%20priorities%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20State%20Department%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrograms%20that%20were%20not%20cut%20included%20food%20assistance%2C%20life-saving%20medical%20treatments%20for%20diseases%20like%20HIV%20and%20malaria%20and%20support%20for%20countries%20including%20Haiti%2C%20Cuba%2C%20Venezuela%20and%20Lebanon%2C%20among%20others%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20a%20federal%20judge%20gave%20the%20Trump%20administration%20less%20than%20two%20days%20to%20unfreeze%20all%20aid%2C%20after%20a%20previous%20court%20order%20issued%20nearly%20two%20weeks%20earlier%20went%20ignored.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trump%20administration%20filed%20a%20petition%20to%20put%20a%20hold%20on%20the%20lower%20court%20order%2C%20which%20was%20granted%20by%20US%20Supreme%20Court%20Chief%20Justice%20John%20Roberts%20late%20Wednesday%2C%20according%20to%20US%20media%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUSAID%2C%20created%20after%20a%20bill%20passed%20by%20Congress%20in%201961%2C%20had%20a%20workforce%20of%20more%20than%2010%2C000%20employees%20prior%20to%20the%20freeze%2C%20which%20sparked%20shock%20and%20dismay%20among%20personnel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20announced%20on%20February%2023%20that%20it%20was%20laying%20off%201%2C600%20of%20its%20employees%20in%20the%20United%20States%20and%20placing%20most%20of%20the%20remaining%20staff%20on%20administrative%20leave.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20election%20campaign%2C%20Trump%20promised%20to%20slash%20federal%20government%20spending%20and%20bureaucracy%2C%20a%20task%20he%20bestowed%20upon%20his%20top%20donor%20and%20close%20advisor%2C%20billionaire%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20as%20part%20of%20the%20newly%20created%20Department%20of%20Government%20Efficiency%20(DOGE).%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740680640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2F1qorip08_donald-trump-reuters_625x300_27_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-cuts-overseas-development-program-budgets-by-more-than-90-state-dept-7810796%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20his%20first%20day%20in%20office%2C%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20signed%20an%20executive%20order%20demanding%20a%20freeze%20on%20all%20US%20foreign%20aid%20for%2090%20days.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-cuts-overseas-development-program-budgets-by-more-than-90-state-de