20is%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20bus%20depots%20of%20the%20Maharashtra%20State%20Road%20Transport%20Corporation%20(MSRTC)%2C%20in%20Pune%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2037-year-old%20accused%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Gunat%20village%20in%20Pune%2C%20is%20named%20in%20half%20a%20dozen%20cases%20of%20theft%2C%20robbery%20and%20chain-snatching%20in%20Pune%20and%20Ahilyanagar%20district.%20He%20has%20been%20out%20on%20bail%20since%202019%20in%20one%20of%20the%20offences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20say%20the%20Swargate%20bus%20stop%20was%20the%20accused's%20usual%20haunt.%20He%20was%2C%20say%20sources%2C%20often%20spotted%20around%20there%20in%20a%20shirt%2C%20sports%20shoes%20and%20a%20mask.%20He%20would%20tell%20people%20around%20the%20bus%20stand%20that%20he%20was%20a%20policeman%2C%20the%20sources%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20survivor%2C%20she%20was%20waiting%20for%20a%20bus%20for%20Phaltan%20in%20Satara%20district%20at%20one%20of%20the%20platforms%20around%205.45%20am%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20when%20the%20accused%20engaged%20her%20in%20conversation%2C%20calling%20her%20'didi'%20(sister)%2C%20and%20said%20the%20bus%20for%20Satara%20had%20arrived%20at%20another%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20took%20her%20to%20an%20empty%20'Shiv%20Shahi'%20AC%20bus%20parked%20elsewhere%20on%20the%20premises.%20As%20the%20lights%20inside%20the%20bus%20were%20not%20on%2C%20she%20hesitated%20to%20get%20in%20but%20the%20man%20convinced%20her%20that%20it%20was%20the%20right%20vehicle.%20The%20accused%20then%20followed%20her%20and%20raped%20her%2C%20the%20woman%2C%20who%20works%20in%20the%20medical%20field%2C%20told%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20residents%20of%20Gunat%20village%2C%20the%20accused%20is%20married%20and%20has%20children.%20He%20also%20has%20a%20brother%20and%20his%20parents%20are%20farm%20labourers%2C%20say%20villagers.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20today%2C%20Maharashtra%20Transport%20Minister%20Pratap%20Sarn