urnalism%2C%20but%20%26quot%3Bbetter%20journalism%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20clarification%20that%20extended%20over%20five%20posts%20on%20social%20media%20platform%20X%2C%20Mr%20Tharoor%20said%20he%20used%20the%20word%20%26quot%3Boption%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20context%20of%20spending%20time%20and%20not%20political%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20%C2%A0said%20i%20had%20multiple%20'options%20to%20spend%20my%20time'%20in%20literary%20pursuits%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%2C%20which%20was%20misinterpreted...%20And%20as%20usual%2C%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20media%20reacted%20to%20the%20headline%20and%20the%20political%20class%20reacted%20to%20the%20media%2C%20and%20I%20was%20left%20dealing%20with%20the%20mess!%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20protection%20does%20a%20public%20figure%20have%20against%20such%20flagrantly%20irresponsible%20journalism...%20no%20one%20spares%20a%20thought%20for%20the%20days%20of%20abuse%2C%20insult%2C%20calumny%20(as%20well%20as%20unexpected%20support%20and%20even%20adulation)%20that%20came%20my%20way%20-%20all%20because%20of%20things%20i%20hadn't%20said%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20another%20of%20his%20posts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Tharoor%20-%20a%20former%20Union%20minister%20and%20a%20four-time%20MP%20from%20Thiruvananthapuram%20--%20had%20upset%20his%20party%20by%20praising%20the%20certain%20policies%20of%20the%20CPM%20in%20Kerala%20and%20the%20state's%20growth.%20But%20he%20clarified%20last%20week%20that%20he%20was%20highlighting%20the%20state's%20progress%20in%20the%20start-up%20sector.%20He%20also%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20he%20would%20pursue%20his%20own%20interests%20if%20the%20party%20did%20not%20want%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20party%20wants%20me%20then%20I%20will%20be%20there%20for%20the%20party.%20If%20not%2C%20I%20have%20my%20own%20things%20to%20do.%20You%20should%20not%20think%20that%20I%20don't%20have%20any%20option%20to%20spend%20time.%20I%20have%20options.%20I%20have%20my%20books%2C%20speeches%2C%20invitations%20from%20across%20the%20world%20for%20talks%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20was%20covered%20by%20many%20media%20organisations%2C%20including%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Tharoor%20today%20said%20the%20experience%20was%20%26quot%3Bhugely%20instructive%20and%20eye-opening%20for%20me%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20this%20kerfuffle%20might%20blow%20over%2C%20it%20has%20brought%20a%20lot%20of%20issues%20out%20into%20the%20open.%20I%20suddenly%20discovered%20what%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20really%20thought%20of%20me%20and%20learned%20from%20others'%20speculations%20about%20options%20that%20i%20hadn't%20ever%20considered%20exercising.%20Some%20people%20woke%20up%20to%20issues%20they%20had%20been%20complacent%20about%20and%20others%20found%20reasons%20to%20vent%20their%20feelings.%20Suddenly%20my%20place%20in%20Indian%20politics%20was%20being%20discussed%20-%20in%20a%20few%20cases%20enlighteningly%20and%20with%20insight%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20posted%20today.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20democracy%20cannot%20do%20without%20a%20free%20press.%20As%20a%20convinced%20democrat%2C%20I%20will%20never%20call%20for%20greater%20regulation%20or%20controls%20on%20the%20media.%20But%20is%20it%20completely%20futile%20to%20hope%20for%20better%20standards%20of%20journalism%20in%20our%20country%3F%20Not%20less%20journalism%20-%20just%20better%20journalism%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20had%20taken%20a%20conscious%20decision%20not%20to%20react%20to%20Mr%20Tharoor's%20comments%20and%20keep%20the%20focus%20on%20Kerala's%20ruling%20LDF%20government%20in%20view%20of%20the%20coming%20state%20elections.%20The%20party%20is%20also%20having%20a%20high-level%20meeting%20in%20Delhi%20on%20Friday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740670680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F2ph2j96g_shashi-tharoor_625x300_30_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22