CWe%20are%20bringing%20it%2C%20making%20sure%20we%20provide%20everything%20to%20ensure%20it%20successfully%20increases%20in%20numbers%20and%20can%20be%20given%20a%20home%20in%20the%20wild%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaCONES%20also%20helps%20Darjeeling%20Zoo%20plan%20its%20conservation%20breeding%20programmes%20by%20screening%20animals%20for%20diseases%20and%20providing%20information%20on%20the%20founder%20populations%E2%80%99%20genetic%20makeup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20holistic%20approach%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20animals%20have%20a%20generation%20time%20%E2%80%94%20the%20period%20from%20birth%20to%20when%20they%20reach%20sexual%20maturity%20and%20produce%20their%20offspring.%20For%20red%20pandas%2C%20this%20is%2018-20%20months.%20But%20in%20the%20wild%2C%20numerous%20constraints%20impact%20this%20process%3A%20high%20mortality%20rates%20among%20the%20young%2C%20challenges%20in%20finding%20mates%2C%20potential%20food%20shortages%20after%20pregnancy%2C%20and%20predation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECaptive%20breeding%20programmes%20aim%20to%20mitigate%20these%20challenges%20by%20providing%20a%20controlled%20environment%20with%20adequate%20food%20and%20protection%20from%20predators%2C%20and%20by%20carefully%20selecting%20breeding%20pairs%20to%20maximise%20genetic%20diversity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FUntitled-design-6_11zon-1740105036.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Darjeeling%20Zoo%20was%20shortlisted%20for%20the%20WAZA%20Conservation%20and%20Environmental%20Sustainability%20Awards%20in%202024%20for%20its%20red%20panda%20conservation%20efforts%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FUntitled-design-6_11zon-1740105036.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2